subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Despite a tournament-record 14 blocked shots from Baylor’s Brittney Griner, it took Melissa Jones and Morghan Medlock to guide Baylor to a win over Georgetown in an anarchic game.
